title: Miss America Highlights Miss New York Wins Red Cup VIDEO
text:
Miss Oklahoma Alex Eppler danced to David Guetta’s “Titanium.” ( VIDEO ) Miss Mississippi sang a Christina Aguilera song. ( VIDEO ) Miss Alabama danced to the Disney song “Let It Go.” ( VIDEO ) Miss Virginia performed opera. ( VIDEO ) Miss Florida danced to the song “Note to God.” ( VIDEO ) One performance that stole social media was Miss Ohio’s zany ventriloquism act. ( VIDEO ) 2) Miss Iowa Aly Olson ( VIDEO ) and and Miss America judge Kathy Ireland ( VIDEO ) couldn’t help showing off their burping skills.
3) One contestant admits that she was told to NOT do a goat impression but she did it anyway. ( WATCH VIDEO HERE )
someone just did a GOAT IMPRESSION; this is even better than the contestant with a crystalline crab shoe #missamerica pic.twitter.com/C3XQwJMiM4

4) Miss Nebraska forgets to close her legs on national television. Social media goes nuts.
Miss Nebraska channeling her inner Sharon Stone from Basic Instinct.
5) The questions were actually tough this year.
Miss Massachusetts was asked about rape on college campuses. ( VIDEO ) Miss Virginia was asked about how to deal with ISIS. ( VIDEO ) Miss Florida was asked about Ray Rice. ( VIDEO ) Miss New York was asked about women in Congress ( VIDEO ) Miss Arkansas was asked about children using guns. ( VIDEO ) Tags: Miss America
